# Email Content Generator using Hugging Face LLAMA2 and Streamlit

![GitHub License](https://img.shields.io/github/license/your-username/Email-Content-Generator-using-Hugging-Face-LLAMA2-and-Streamlit)

This project is a simple web application that uses Hugging Face's LLAMA2, a powerful language model, and Streamlit, a Python library for creating web apps, to generate email content. It can be helpful for generating drafts, templates, or content for emails when you need some inspiration or assistance.

